nodes.text: A Selanikio Sportster was a model of landspeeder. Considered old in 2 BBY, it was an open-cockpit design propelled by an Aratech Arrow engine. Veeka Gault owned a Selanikio Sportster shortly after the end of the Clone Wars before crashing it into Annileen Calwell's X-31. Biggs Darklighter owned one as a young man on Tatooine.
